FBIS4-39198 "drsov109_p_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-109 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Further on Shelling of Northern Border Further on Shelling of Northern Border NC0606134594 Yerevan Armenia's Radio First Program Network in Armenian 1300 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606134594 Yerevan Armenia's Radio First Program Network in Armenian 1300 GMT 6 Jun 94 Armenian BFN [Text] Armenian Defense Ministry press service reported that the Azerbaijani Army continued its aggressive operations against the border in Noyemberyanskiy Rayon last night. The enemy shelled the defensive positions around Berdavan with infantry fighting vehicles and large-caliber guns between 2400-0240. There were no casualties. Our border guards abided by the cease-fire agreement and did not retaliate. The same source reported a half an hour ago that the enemy resumed the shelling of (?Mertsavan) in Noyemberyanskiy Rayon as of 0600 this morning. They used various types of weapons [words indistinct]. The shelling continued sporadically throughout the day. There are no casualties. The Armenian side (?did not) retaliate.
